<li>Inhale and engage your core. Exhale and curl the bar towards your shoulders.&nbsp;</li>



<li>Pause briefly at the top position, squeezing both biceps.</li>



<li>Inhale and lower the bar back to the starting position under control.</li>



<li>Keep your upper arms against the pad with your chest up and head facing forward throughout.</li>
