<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Bicep-Curl">Dumbbell Bicep Curl</h3>



<p>When done correctly with your elbows tucked in, <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/cable-preacher-curl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">dumbbell bicep curls</a> teach the foundational elbow flexion movement and provide a great stimulus.</p>



